  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; required and achieved levels are reported. The ContextOfUse prose references operating flow-speed combinations and clinical thresholds, but no structured applicability constraint or operating envelope object is linked, leaving the formal boundary of model validity unspecified.",
